| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3382 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0041f4cc-65d4-5b49-8d9c-ef2aac93705e"
